Summary: Woman kicked an entity in her bedroom.
divs: sighting detailsa woman awoke to see a light on her bedroom ceiling and three entities standingby the bed, each 3 1\2 feet tall and floating above the floor. she kicked one inthe chest. it felt light and flew backward, landing on its hindside. she thenlost consciousness and remembers nothing more.
